{"id":245623,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-贵州黎庆洪案看守所设置障碍阻挡律师会/","date":"2012-08-08T04:31:49Z","modified":"2012-08-08T04:31:49Z","title":"维权网 | 贵州黎庆洪案看守所设置障碍阻挡律师会见当事人（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日上午</span><span>，贵州“黎庆洪涉黑案”辩护团王誓华律师前往</span><span>贵阳市白云区看守会见自己的当事人蔡峰讨论</span><span>上</span><span>诉事宜，看守所接待的工作人员说监管支队和法院出了文件，其中提到的律师不许会见。如下图是贴在工作人员左手边的名单，其中还有另一位辩护团成员杨学林律师。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王誓华律师要求给出不让接见的相关文件或理由，将会就此起诉相关部门，并要求赔偿机票损失。在王誓华律师的坚持下，经过工作人员向上级请示，等</span><span>候了两个多小时后最终被允许会见。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王誓华律师在此间被要求单独会见，而不允许蔡峰的另一辩护人汪律师一同会见。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kmhs-mowHtM/UCHkinCxQXI/AAAAAAAALFA/m6qudK-0ZF0/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-kmhs-mowHtM/UCHkinCxQXI/AAAAAAAALFA/m6qudK-0ZF0/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vWCoGXmbls4/UCHkkbadfMI/AAAAAAAALFI/gXOTuiluShg/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"186\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vWCoGXmbls4/UCHkkbadfMI/AAAAAAAALFI/gXOTuiluShg/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6054391238765471823?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br 